data.title: Paul Heyse In Paradise 1878 2 Vols German Literature Nobel Prize Winner
data.meta_description: Heyse was a giant of mid to late 19th century German literature and was awarded the Nobel Prize for literature in 1910. Spines tanned, cloth lightly rubbed and soiled, but a nice solid set of a scarce work.
